      • getReverse

        public abstract MatchField<T> getReverse()
        Returns the reverse match field. For example for a MatchField matching on source ip 1.1.1.1 it will return a MatchField matching on destination IP 1.1.1.1. For not reversable MatchField, a copy of this MatchField will be returned
        Returns:
        the correspondent reverse MatchField object or a copy of this object if the field is not reversable
